data.text:
Oak Hill, West Virginia

The gas station where Hank Williams was discovered dead in the back seat of a Cadillac stood here until early 2007. The city of Oak HIll decided not to convert the station into a museum.

Monument across the street:

www.flickr.com/photos/auvet/1055072161/in/photostream/
